lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsosad.gif&h=5e5c7195&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1494614/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1494614/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>睇完依條片你班社會垃圾仲有咩好講 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1294350453913612/posts/2902067653141876/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1294350453913612%2Fposts%2F2902067653141876%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=da24c606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1294350453913612/posts/2902067653141876/?sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n唔計收錢做野果班，根本由頭到尾你地就係為發洩而出黎破壞，為自由？我呸<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2F369.gif&h=ceeaab40&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1469638/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1469638/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>忍撚咗你班撚樣好耐,終於有得笑 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>成班白卡連登仔又講到end game又天安門眼鏡仔又最最後一次抗爭又盛<br />\n你老尾智力正常少少既係屋企涼緊冷氣啦<br />\n俾人利用點你出黎幫人賺錢仲係度扮撚晒有料咁<br />\n條例過咗關你撚事咩,你普通到無撚得再普通<br />\n邊撚個會理你條柒頭呀,拉你返去槍斃都嫌晒子彈啦,蟻民<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2F369.gif&h=ceeaab40&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1195488/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1195488/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/kBN5bas.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"6715b8bcca